lyrics:
[Verse]
I'm on my journey, feeling lost in the dark
Every step I take, leaves a deep impact on my heart
Tears flow like a river, emotions running wild
Searching for answers, through this twisted mile

[Chorus]
Aching soul, healing scars in the night
These easy lyrics, bring emotions to light
Through the pain, I find my strength inside
Let these words guide me, on this emotional ride
